  "body": "<p><em>Happy Friday! If you're an email subscriber, be sure to check your email as we have a FREE DIGITAL PRINT for you I'm so excited to have launched </em><em>Hustle &amp; Heart in our shop</em><em> and I whipped up an exclusive design!</em></p><p>Hello everyone! It’s <a href=\"http://abstractinspiration.com/\">Zinia</a> here and today I want to share with you another layout I created featuring the fun and colorful Hustle &amp; Heart collection designed by Amy.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595296338812-5FQ38L2KVGDKCJ80ZA2I/3a-Zinia-Sept-UnderTheSea-01.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I am madly in love with this collection and all the bright and whimsical designs that it features. The patterns are so inspiring that in many cases it’s so easy to base a whole page on just the beautiful papers of this collection.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595296359386-6MBPUAVP2N2PW74BKSY1/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For this layout I started with the beautiful patchwork paper and I cut out all the areas that had blue and orange patterns. I used three different sizes of circle punches to create a bunch of bubbles.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595296379878-EKKERZF9O8NGXT8MNHOC/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The main idea was to create a scenery that gives an impression of an underwater scape. For the top and the bottom of the page I fussy-cut strips of other patterns to create an impression of ground and sky/ocean.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595296410817-V6YW9XY7F9LZT220AUMC/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I kept the embellishing part fairly simple using a few color coordinating items like my absolute favorite suede bows, puffy hearts and a few clear stickers.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595296439070-XV6J4DFQWLULNF615LF0/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Zinia<br/><a href=\"http://abstractinspiration.com/\">Abstract Inspiration Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/abstractinspiration/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AbstractInsp\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbstractInspirationPage\">Facebook</a></p><p><em>Thanks so much for sharing this layout with us, Zinia! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/?category=amy+tangerine+design+team\"><em>here</em></a><em>. Shop HUSTLE &amp; HEART now on </em><em>our shop site</em><em>! YAY!</em></p><p><strong>SUPPLIES USED:</strong></p><p>341870 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper - Across The Waves | 340875 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper - Hello Sunrise | 340877 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper - Patchwork Show | 341885 Hustle &amp; Heart - LAYERED PAPER STICKERS | 341884 Hustle &amp; Heart - STICKER BOOK | 341889 Hustle &amp; Heart - PUFFY HEARTS | 341893 Hustle &amp; Heart - MINI FAUX SUEDE BOWS | 376225 Oh Happy Life - RUBBER SHAPES</p><p><em>Disclosure: Some of the links above are affiliate links. I receive a small percentage of sales at no cost to you. My creative partners and I really appreciate your continued support and every little bit helps me to bring you consistent content!</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
